Package: historicaldata
Title: Historical Finance Data via DuckDB and Parquet
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("John", "Gavin", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "john@example.com")
Description: Code-only R package providing access to historical OHLCV data
    for equities, crypto, macro series, and factor returns. Data is stored
    as Parquet on Hugging Face Datasets and queried via DuckDB httpfs with
    predicate pushdown. No data is bundled — the package ships access
    functions and a dataset registry.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
